<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>
        @{
            ViewData["Title"] = "Home Page";
        }
    </title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/Index.css" asp-append-version="true" />
    <script src="~/lib/jquery/jquery.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
<div class="text-center">
    <h1 class="display-4">Welcome</h1>
</div>
<div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
    <ol class="carousel-indicators">
        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="3"></li>
        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="4"></li>
    </ol>
    <div class="carousel-inner">
        <div class="carousel-item active">
            <img src="/images/sacrament1.jpeg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Image 1">
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="/images/sacrament2.jpeg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Image 2">
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="/images/sacrament3.jpeg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Image 3">
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="/images/sacrament4.jpeg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Image 4">
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="/images/sacrament5.jpeg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Image 5">
        </div>
    </div>
    <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
    </a>
    <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
    </a>
</div>

<script>
        $(document).ready(function () {
            $('.carousel-control-prev').click(function () {
                $('#carouselExampleIndicators').carousel('prev');
            });
            $('.carousel-control-next').click(function () {
                $('#carouselExampleIndicators').carousel('next');
            });
        });
</script>

<div class="text-center">
    <br />
    <p>Welcome to our sacrament planner website, the ultimate solution for planning successful sacrament meetings!</p>
    <p>Whether you're an experienced pro or novice, we're here to help you make it a success.</p>
    <br />
    <br />
    <p>Our website is designed to make sacrament meeting planning easy, efficient, and stress-free.</p>
    <p>We offer a wide range of tools and resources that you can use to plan your meetings from start to finish.</p>
    <p>From Hymn selection to speaker count and benediction, we've got you covered.</p>
    <br />
    <br />
    <p>Our team of experienced programmers and web developers is always available to provide you with guidance and support throughout the planning process.</p>
    <p>We understand every ward is unique, and we work closely with the Bishopric to ensure that our sacrament meeting planner is tailored to your specific needs and requirements.</p>
    <br />
    <br />
    <p>At our sacrament planner website we're committed to providing you with the best possible service and support.</p>
    <p>We're constantly updating our website with new features and tools to make your sacrament planning experience even better.</p>
    <br />
    <br />
    <p>Thank you for choosing our sacrament planner website. We look forward to working with you and making your sacrament meeting a success!</p>
</div>
</body>
</html>
